Name:           OOKiedokie
Version:        0.0.0+git.20151230
Release:        0
Summary:        A tool for transmitting and receiving OOK-modulated data with SDRs
License:        MIT
Url:            https://github.com/jynik/OOKiedokie
Source:         %{name}-%{version}.tar.xz
